{"tid":1209571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook 有個friend 走入我個post 到引戰","createTime":"2019-06-12T11:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T13:27:01.000Z","uid":22575,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f51f8514f1046893c4d9dcf1a67b7fa95a6f7060","tid":1209571,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"話説我今日見到咁多警犬對香港市民既不人道對待，就share 左其中一段去宣洩自己既憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n之後過左一陣，其中一個facebook friend 走左入黎留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fxD9OPH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfxD9OPH.png&h=3b12eaa5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SxasAuJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxasAuJ.png&h=3498dddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到今日既示威人士咁樣為香港付岀，佢居然講d 咁既野當然唔忿氣，於是我就反駁返佢，加多兩條警犬亂打人既video<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/447VKo7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F447VKo7.png&h=c7abd07a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QKNyv4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQKNyv4b.png&h=8e1a737a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後我再睇佢facebook, 原來佢仲post 左呢d 野<br />\n<br />\n仲要好似係警犬黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gT3qnbt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgT3qnbt.png&h=c1baaf84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b494a1ff55c19b590c41e50f0f3baa05f46bc5","tid":1209571,"uid":224857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:53:36.000Z","msg":"康文正？"},{"pid":"475167370619b25a80e3762e335724ce9fb52560","tid":1209571,"uid":118851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"98b494a1ff55c19b590c41e50f0f3baa05f46bc5","tid":1209571,"uid":224857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T11:53:36.000Z","msg":"康文